data.eml:eml: A new, prairie-restricted species of Anacampsis Curtis (Lepidoptera: Gelechiidae) from Illinois

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Harrison, Terry L., Berenbaum, May R. (2013): A new, prairie-restricted species of Anacampsis Curtis (Lepidoptera: Gelechiidae) from Illinois. Zootaxa 3741 (1): 194-200, DOI: http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.3741.1.8
